"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.7\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.7</span> 标题：捆、禾捆（sheaf）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֲלֻמָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’alumah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:6\">PSA 126:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עָמִיר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘amir)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:21\">JER 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:13\">AMO 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:6\">ZEC 12:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עמר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘imer（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:7\">PSA 129:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֹמֶר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘omer)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:12\">LEV 23:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:15\">LEV 23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:19\">DEU 24:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:7\">RUT 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:15\">RUT 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:10\">JOB 24:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：δράγμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dragma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt8:3\">JDT 8:3</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0934_sheaf.jpg\" alt=\"收获的谷穗\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">收获的谷穗 ( Jakub Hałun © Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>禾捆是将收割下来的农作物的秆和穗子捆在一起而形成的束，通常就用农作物的秆来捆扎。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>收割谷物时，可以用镰刀贴近地面将其割下来（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.6 镰刀 (sickle)&lt;REALIA:1.1.6&gt;</a> ），或者用手拔出来。然后，把许多谷物的秆拢成束，在中间将其捆扎起来，成为一捆。如果这些禾捆不是立即搬走，那么可以竖立在地上，以免穗子接触潮湿的地面。把禾捆聚拢到一起后，就可以送去禾场（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.8.1 禾场 (threshing floor)&lt;REALIA:1.1.8.1&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在翻译“禾捆”一词时，翻译者可以使用描述性的短语，例如“一束收获的谷物”。在有些文化中，人们并不知道将谷物捆成捆的做法。有些语言可能必须采用“捆在一起的谷物”这类短语来表达。有些经文需要具体指明是哪种谷物。有时，翻译者需要将“禾捆”宽泛地翻译成“庄稼”（“harvest”，如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:6\">PSA 126:6</a> ；比较<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:10\">JOB 24:10</a> 中的译词，“wheat”“小麦”），甚至译成“谷物”（“grain”，如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:13\">AMO 2:13</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在比较宽泛的意义上翻译“禾捆”的另一处经文是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt8:3\">JDT 8:3</a> 。这节经文的原文直译为：“当他站在那里，监督那些在田间捆禾捆的人的时候”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 采用了直译，但<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 英文直译作“在地里监督农民的时候”。</p>\n<p>实际上，希伯来文<em>‘amir</em> 和<em>‘omer</em> 是指放在田边的许多禾捆形成的堆，还没有被送到禾场，因此<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:13\">AMO 2:13</a> 的重点是在谷物的总重量。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
